      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Wind Speed Wyvern",
        "Client": "Neighboring Hamlet\u0027s Envoy",
        "Description": "Nargacuga are so cool, right?\r\nAnd fast too! How is it that\r\nthey are so light on their feet!?\r\nI MUST know! I bet if I made\r\nsome Nargacuga shoes I could\r\nbe just as fast as they are!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Wyverne \u00E9clair",
        "Client": "Envoy\u00E9 du hameau voisin",
        "Description": "Les Nargacuga sont trop cool,\r\net rapides en plus ! Je me\r\ndemande bien comment ils font\r\npour aller aussi vite...\r\nSi j\u0027arrivais \u00E0 faire des\r\nchaussures en Nargacuga,\r\nj\u0027irais aussi vite qu\u0027eux !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Wyvern veloce come il vento",
        "Client": "Emissario di Hamlet",
        "Description": "Forti i Nargacuga, vero?\r\nE sono anche super veloci!\r\nVorrei tanto sapere come fanno\r\na correre cos\u00EC. Scommetto che,\r\nse avessi delle scarpe di\r\nNargacuga, sarei rapido\r\ncome loro!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Wyvern in Windeseile",
        "Client": "Bote aus dem Nachbarort",
        "Description": "Nargacuga sind so cool, oder?\r\nUnd schnell! Wie sind sie nur\r\nso leichtf\u00FC\u00DFig? Ich MUSS es\r\nwissen! Ich wette, mit Narga-\r\ncuga-Schuhen an den F\u00FC\u00DFen w\u00E4re\r\nich genauso schnell wie sie!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Nargacuga.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Wyvern como el viento",
        "Client": "Enviado de aldea vecina",
        "Description": "Nargacuga es m\u00E1s r\u00E1pido que el\r\nt\u00EDo m\u00E1s r\u00E1pido que conozco:\r\nyo. Quiero tener su velocidad.\r\n\u00A1Necesito unas zapas con sus\r\nmateriales para desentra\u00F1ar su\r\nsecreto! Te lo ruego, \u00A1caza\r\nuno por m\u00ED!",
        "Target": "Caza un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0412\u0438\u0432\u0435\u0440\u043D\u0430, \u0431\u044B\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u044F, \u043A\u0430\u043A \u0432\u0435\u0442\u0435\u0440",
        "Client": "\u041F\u043E\u0441\u043B\u0430\u043D\u043D\u0438\u043A \u0431\u043B\u0438\u0436\u043D\u0435\u0439 \u0434\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0432\u043D\u0438",
        "Description": "\u041D\u0430\u0440\u0433\u0430\u043A\u0443\u0433\u0438 \u043A\u0440\u0443\u0442\u044B\u0435, \u0441\u043A\u0430\u0436\u0438?\r\n\u0418 \u0431\u044B\u0441\u0442\u0440\u044B\u0435! \u041A\u0430\u043A \u0438\u043C \u0443\u0434\u0430\u0435\u0442\u0441\u044F\r\n\u043D\u0430\u0431\u0438\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044C \u0442\u0430\u043A\u0443\u044E \u0441\u043A\u043E\u0440\u043E\u0441\u0442\u044C?!\r\n\u042F \u0414\u041E\u041B\u0416\u0415\u041D \u044D\u0442\u043E \u0443\u0437\u043D\u0430\u0442\u044C!\r\n\u0415\u0441\u043B\u0438 \u044F \u0441\u0434\u0435\u043B\u0430\u044E \u0441\u0435\u0431\u0435 \u043E\u0431\u0443\u0432\u044C\r\n\u0438\u0437 \u0438\u0445 \u043A\u043E\u0436\u0438, \u044F \u0441\u0442\u0430\u043D\u0443 \u0442\u0430\u043A\u0438\u043C \u0436\u0435\r\n\u0431\u044B\u0441\u0442\u0440\u044B\u043C!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041D\u0430\u0440\u0433\u0430\u043A\u0443\u0433\u0443",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
